metadata.name: YOURSKULL
metadata.description:
The Your Skull World are NFTs stored on Ethereum blockchain. Each skull is a unique art with specific characteristic.

For us, it is more than a job. It is our passion, our purpose, our lifestyle. We believe that our purpose is to take a client's business to new heights. We change the way people think about digital art. We are artists with a purpose. We are a new generation of art and business in the industry.
